metadata.name: RK#1
metadata.description:
飼い主さんの影響でビールにハマった犬けんちゃんが「自宅でリラックスしてビールを楽しむ」をコンセプトに手描き感とシンプルな2色構成で展開するコレクションです。

This collection is based on the concept of "relaxing and enjoying beer at home" by Ken-chan, a dog who got hooked on beer under the influence of his owner, with a hand-drawn feel and simple two-color composition.
